        </item>
        <item>
            <title>【MWC 2024】勁量 28,000 mAh 超大電智能電話，可待機逾 90 日、通話時間 122 小時</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/28/energizer-28000-mah-mobile/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=energizer-28000-mah-mobile</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/28/energizer-28000-mah-mobile/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 13:00:38 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提電話]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Energizer]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1221668</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>著名的電池生產商 Energizer（勁量）在 2020 年 MWC 上曾發布過一款待機長達 50 日的手機，今日 Energizer 再創新猷，於 MWC 2024 發布一款電池容量達 28,000mAh 的手機，號稱全球最大電池容量的手機，據悉其待機時間長達 94 天。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221685" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dscf0349-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dscf0349-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dscf0349.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>這部手提電話實際上並非 Energizer 製造，而是由 Avenir Telecom 經 Energizer 授權下使用該品牌推出，型號為 Hard Case P28K。能夠稱自己為「Hard Case」，顧名思義，這款電話防護等級非常高，達到 IP69。製造商聲稱 P28K 電源足以使用一星期，方便經常要到野外的人。P28K 額定通話時間為 122 小時，而待機時間則長達 2252 小時，換算約為 94 日。</p><p>除續航力驚人，其充電效率亦非常高。這部電話支援 33W 高速充電，而且據製造商表示，如果使用原廠 36W 充電器的話，將能夠在 1.5 小時內充滿電。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221686" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dscf0342-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dscf0342-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dscf0342.jpg 828w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>不過這部電話的缺點是其機身非常「有份量」，厚度達 27.8 mm，重量更有 570 克，差不多等於 3 部 iPhone 15 。除了機身厚重之外，其規格亦比較陽春。P28K 使用 MediaTek MT6789 核心，配備 8GB RAM，256 GB 儲存，其螢幕則是 6.78 吋 1080p LCD 螢幕。</p><p>Avenir Telecom 計劃在今年 10 月推出這部電話，初步定價為 249.99 歐羅（約港幣 2,122.78 元），據悉這部電話將會在美國以外的市場推出。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/25/24082954/avenir-telecom-energizer-hard-case-p28k-28000mah-smartphone">The Verge</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/29/apple-working-on-beats-solo-4-headphones/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple 推出 iOS 17.4RC 版，揭 Beats Solo 4 正在開發中</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/28/apple-car-plan-ends/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple 電動車計劃壽終正寢   2,000 名員工受影響</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/27/iphone-finewoven-peel-like-banana/mobile-phone/phone-parts/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">iPhone FineWoven 保護套被外媒批評，容易褪色甩皮狀況如爛香蕉</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/28/energizer-28000-mah-mobile/mobile-phone/">【MWC 2024】勁量 28,000 mAh 超大電智能電話，可待機逾 90 日、通話時間 122 小時</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/28/energizer-28000-mah-mobile/mobile-phone/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>【MWC 2024】OPPO Air Glass 3 智能眼鏡加入 AI「AndesGPT」    戴眼鏡開會即總結會議要點</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/28/oppo-air-glasses/vr-mr-ar/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=oppo-air-glasses</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/28/oppo-air-glasses/vr-mr-ar/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 11:53:48 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[VR 科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AI]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[oppo]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[OPPO Air Glass 3 XR]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1221787</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>OPPO 近日在世界流動通訊大會（Mobile World Congress，MWC）發布全新「輔助實境智能眼鏡」OPPO Air Glass 3 概念產品，據官方資料顯示，OPPO Air Glass 3 能夠利用手機專屬 App 使用 AI 大模型 AndesGPT。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221788" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img02-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img02-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img02.jpg 800w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲OPPO Air Glass 3，圖片來源：OPPO</p><p>OPPO 表示，Air Glass 3 XR 現階段屬概念產品，重量僅在 50g 左右，採用 OPPO 自主研發的樹脂晶圓衍射光波導鏡片，折射率高達 1.70，顯示亮度均勻性大於 50%，入眼峯值亮度超過 1000 尼特。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221789" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221794" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-5-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-5-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-5.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221791" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-2-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-2-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-2.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲OPPO 示範影片可見， Air Glass 3 XR 能顯示不少資訊</p><p>OPPO 官方表示，使用者可利用手機裏的 OPPO Air Glass 3 專屬應用程式，開啟旗下自主研發的 AI 大模型 AndesGPT。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221790" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-1-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-1-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-1.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲OPPO Air Glass 3 專屬應用程式</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221796" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-7-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-7-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-7.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲輕觸眼鏡的鏡臂就能夠使用語音助理功能</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221795" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-6-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-6-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-6.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲OPPO Air Glass 3 XR 實際佩戴</p><p style="text-align: left;">雖然 OPPO 這款 XR 眼鏡看起來非常高科技，而且官方示範影片裏面出現的功能亦很實用，OPPO 方面尚未透露 Air Glass 3 XR 上市時間表，因此就讓我們拭目以待吧。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_28703"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/SedimxtA73g?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p style="text-align: left;">資料來源：<a href="https://www.oppo.com/cn/newsroom/press/514/">OPPO</a>、<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SedimxtA73g">Oppo@YouTube</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/06/oppo-find-n3-flip-review/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】OPPO Find N3 Flip　外形　手感　鉸位　功能　屏幕　相機　效能開箱評測</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/28/nokia-and-oppo-sign-crosslicense-5g-patent-agreement/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">OPPO 與 Nokia 簽訂專利交叉授權，終止長達兩年訴訟戰</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/28/oppo-air-glasses/vr-mr-ar/">【MWC 2024】OPPO Air Glass 3 智能眼鏡加入 AI「AndesGPT」    戴眼鏡開會即總結會議要點</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
